snippet.title: Vasara Collection - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
QuByte Interactive and VISCO Corporation teamed up to bring Vasara Collection to PC and consoles. This game is a compilation that includes both Vasara (2000) and Vasara 2 (2001) arcade games, as well as a new Timeless Mode.

Vasara, Vasara 2 (C) VISCO Corporation
Vasara Collection developed and published by QuByte Interactive
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1085630/VASARA_Collection/
